### ========================================
### ActivityType API
### ========================================

### Отримати всі типи активності
GET https://localhost:7001/api/ActivityType
Accept: application/json

### Створити тип активності
POST https://localhost:7001/api/ActivityType
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "activityTypeName": "IT та розробка програмного забезпечення"
}

### Отримати тип активності за ID
GET https://localhost:7001/api/ActivityType/{{activityTypeId}}
Accept: application/json

### ========================================
### Companie API
### ========================================

### Отримати всі компанії
GET https://localhost:7001/api/Companie
Accept: application/json

### Створити компанію
POST https://localhost:7001/api/Companie
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "companyName": "Tech Solutions Ltd",
  "emailCompany": "info@techsolutions.com",
  "address": "вул. Шевченка, 123, Київ",
  "phone": "+380441234567",
  "activityTypeId": "{{activityTypeId}}"
}

### Отримати компанію за ID
GET https://localhost:7001/api/Companie/{{companyId}}
Accept: application/json

### ========================================
### Worker API
### ========================================

### Отримати всіх працівників
GET https://localhost:7001/api/Worker
Accept: application/json

### Створити працівника
POST https://localhost:7001/api/Worker
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
